"0"/></target></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="4"/><sdl:cxt id="5"/><sdl:cxt id="2"/><sdl:cxt id="3"/><sdl:node id="3"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="2b0cbf26-483f-40c6-8a43-c13bdb619ed0"><source>Pain de Sucre : pâtisserie artisanale et créative depuis 2004</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Pain de Sucre : pâtisserie artisanale et créative depuis 2004</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Pain de Sucre: pastelería artesanal y creativa desde 2004</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="1" conf="Translated" origin="tm" origin-system="PainDeSucre" percent="100" text-match="SourceAndTarget"><sdl:value key="created_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_on">01/13/2025 12:45:44</sdl:value><sdl:value key="modified_on">01/13/2025 21:30:37</sdl:value><sdl:value key="last_modified_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SDL:OriginalTranslationHash">-1500574621</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">rfpG/LoaJdkmuu21q5wbuNsu1TtB07ODIdgtA766Rnk=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="6"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit translate="no" id="d1129b3e-a619-4455-84a8-f8b501f222a0"><source/></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="7"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="0c9e372a-4124-451e-8f28-f9b7edaa0417"><source>Retrouvez en ligne l&apos;offre sucrée et salée de la pâtisserie Pain de Sucre. Passez commande avant 23h puis retirez vos articles en magasin le lendemain dès 10h.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">Retrouvez en ligne l&apos;offre sucrée et salée de la pâtisserie Pain de Sucre.</mrk> <mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">Passez commande avant 23h puis retirez vos articles en magasin le lendemain dès 10h.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">Encuentra online la oferta dulce y salada de la pastelería Pain de Sucre.</mrk> <mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">Haz tu pedido antes de las 23:00 h y recoge tus productos en tienda a partir de las 10:00 h del día siguiente.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="2" conf="Translated" origin="interactive" percent="100" text-match="SourceAndTarget"><sdl:prev-origin origin="tm" origin-system="PainDeSucre" percent="100" text-match="SourceAndTarget"><sdl:prev-origin/><sdl:value key="created_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_on">01/13/2025 21:30:47</sdl:value><sdl:value key="modified_on">01/14/2025 23:36:40</sdl:value><sdl:value key="last_modified_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SDL:OriginalTranslationHash">264005823</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">7d60ga6zTrQBdLqaMv+EIUhOT+9wnAkn9Q8PBmBYc+Q=</sdl:value></sdl:prev-origin><sdl:value key="created_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_on">01/13/2025 21:30:47</sdl:value><sdl:value key="modified_on">01/17/2025 16:56:26</sdl:value><sdl:value key="last_modified_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SDL:OriginalTranslationHash">-638228838</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">7d60ga6zTrQBdLqaMv+EIUhOT+9wnAkn9Q8PBmBYc+Q=</sdl:value></sdl:seg><sdl:seg id="3" conf="Translated" origin="interactive"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">J7fkXK1yl54GrYlNk4FNSmRZK37F73MnZYDTT2J1B8M=</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_on">01/15/2025 14:37:52</sdl:value><sdl:value key="last_modified_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="modified_on">01/17/2025 08:29:34</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SDL:OriginalTranslationHash">-284807932</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="8"/><sdl:cxt id="2"/><sdl:cxt id="3"/><sdl:node id="2"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="c630c04d-0b64-4900-9ce5-88b42ab973df"><source><x id="1"/></source><seg-source><x id="1"/></seg-source><target><x id="1"/></target></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="9"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit translate="no" id="995d2834-3d7b-46b8-813d-f59dce32768d"><source/></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="10"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="0c83d