rk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="23" conf="Translated" origin="tm" origin-system="PainDeSucre" percent="100" text-match="SourceAndTarget"><sdl:value key="created_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_on">01/13/2025 22:16:28</sdl:value><sdl:value key="modified_on">01/13/2025 22:17:00</sdl:value><sdl:value key="last_modified_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SDL:OriginalTranslationHash">-1630419732</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">6N2kRP5Ejc0XkQHcnby0N4EkK+MpEjKdvkBbLjVgVwo=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="57"/><sdl:cxt id="48"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="46"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="26"/><sdl:cxt id="3"/><sdl:node id="45"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="7a55c282-5140-4e58-b1a4-d6bf029dc394"><source>Une gamme salée pour vos déjeuners et réceptions</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="24">Une gamme salée pour vos déjeuners et réceptions</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="24">Una gama salada para tus desayunos y visitas</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="24" conf="Translated" origin="tm" origin-system="PainDeSucre" percent="100"><sdl:value key="created_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_on">01/13/2025 22:17:01</sdl:value><sdl:value key="modified_on">01/13/2025 22:17:46</sdl:value><sdl:value key="last_modified_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SDL:OriginalTranslationHash">-906014555</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">xkV8kod09Z0Oho/6+qoyNLVy7kFeKmCj3lib81m+2vw=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="58"/><sdl:cxt id="39"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="46"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="26"/><sdl:cxt id="3"/><sdl:node id="46"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="a74f566e-c63f-4940-8467-cee548abe247"><source>Tous les appétits seront satisfaits grâce à notre offre gourmande de pâtisseries salées, notre alléchante sélection de soupes et salades légères et originales, ou encore nos plats de grande tradition culinaire française revisitée.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="25">Tous les appétits seront satisfaits grâce à notre offre gourmande de pâtisseries salées, notre alléchante sélection de soupes et salades légères et originales, ou encore nos plats de grande tradition culinaire française revisitée.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="25">Todos los apetitos quedarán satisfechos gracias a nuestra deliciosa propuesta de repostería salada, nuestra apetecible selección de sopas y ensaladas ligeras y originales, o incluso nuestros platos de gran tradición culinaria francesa adaptada.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="25" conf="Translated" origin="interactive"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">4MP016eYCiAiglZ+fNVsoxUEstVYcHISpaWAeNYIgsQ=</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_on">01/15/2025 14:38:50</sdl:value><sdl:value key="last_modified_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="modified_on">01/15/2025 14:38:50</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SDL:OriginalTranslationHash">1005538333</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="59"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="46"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="32"/><sdl:cxt id="26"/><sdl:cxt id="3"/><sdl:node id="48"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="1f59c138-e7a9-4d43-9776-a709d5897b30"><source><g id="64"><g id="62">Découvrir</g></g></source><seg-source><g id="64"><g id="62"><mrk mtype="seg" mid="26">Découvrir</mrk></g></g></seg-source><target><g id="64"><g id="62"><mrk mtype="seg" mid="26">Descubrir</mrk></g></g></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="26" co